  "text": "The NMF as a clustering method can be traced back to the work by Lee & Seung [CITATION_1] . But, the first work that explicitly demonstrates it is the work by Xu et al. [CITATION_2] in which they show that the NMF outperforms the spectral methods in term of purity and mutual information measures for Reuters and TDT2 datasets.",
